        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<style>\n@import url(\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@500;700&display=swap\");\n.dashboard-page {\n  background-color: #040508 !important;\n  background-image:\n    linear-gradient(rgba(0,242,254,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),\n    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,242,254,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px) !important;\n  background-size: 30px 30px !important;\n  font-family: \"Rajdhani\", sans-serif !important;\n}\n.panel-container {\n  background: rgba(6,8,16,0.85) !important;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(0,242,254,0.2) !important;\n  border-radius: 4px !important;\n  transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n}\n.panel-container:hover {\n  border-color: rgba(0,242,254,0.5) !important;\n  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,242,254,0.08) !important;\n}\n.panel-title { color: #A0B0C0 !important; font-size: 13px !important; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 1px; }\n</style>\n<div style=\"display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;height:100%;padding:0 20px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,242,254,0.08) 0%,transparent 100%);border-left:4px solid #00F2FE;border-radius:4px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;letter-spacing:3px;text-shadow:0 0 10px #00F2FE;margin:0;\">APEX <span style=\"color:#00F2FE;\">COMMAND</span> <span style=\"color:#8899aa;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\">// </span></h1>\n  <div style=\"display:flex;gap:20px;\">\n    <a href=\"/d/ims-noc-overview\" style=\"color:#00FF87;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid rgba(0,255,135,0.3);background:rgba(0,255,135,0.05);border-radius:4px;\">NOC</a> <a href=\"/d/ims-engineering\" style=\"color:#8899aa;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:4px;\">ENG</a> <a href=\"/d/ims-capacity\" style=\"color:#8899aa;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 12px;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:4px;\">CAP</a>\n  </div>\n</div>"
      },
